author: maintainer-agent
estimated_minutes: 120
acceptance_criteria: "ready[] in pm next --json is ordered by the exact comparator used to pick recommended (priority-first plus existing tie-breakers) with a regression spec covering the GH-513 repro (p0 recommended, ready strictly p1,p2,p3); help text and docs match actual behavior; decision recorded whether per-row rank/reasons are exposed; GH-513 closed"
